VSo in 2011, I altered my name
p4
aVso that I could participate in Far Right youth camp in Hungary.
p5
aVI was doing a PhD looking at youth political socialization \u2014
p6
aVwhy young people were developing political ideologies
p7
aVin a post-communist setting,
p8
aVand I saw that a lot of young people I was talking to
p9
aVwere joining the Far Right,
p10
aVand this was astounding to me.
p11
aVSo I wanted to enroll in this youth camp
p12
aVto get a better understanding of why people were joining.
p13
aa(lp14
VSo a colleague enrolled me,
p15
aVand my last name sounds a little bit too Jewish.
p16
aVSo Erin got turned into Iréna,
p17
aVand Saltman got turned into Sós,
p18
aVwhich means "salty" in Hungarian.
p19
aVAnd in Hungarian, your last name goes first,
